td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bad News</span><hr size=1> Report from Common land<br>
New inky camp in the west common. Not just a group of those darky but tents and materials. After sending them back to hell, first surprise no faction hit! Second one they where not ready to attack me but just threatening. They had just some money on them, unfortunatly during the fight the priestress was going backward under my hits and she died inside the tent by the way it was not possible to loot the corpse. A lieutenant said as i was engaging him i fight something that he is from Indigo brotherhood...<br>
Report from Beffelen<br>
Again a lot of inky... and almost all creatures in this place have new names. One had a madaillon (magic lore no drop) with racial restriction to dark elves, orgres, trolls and very stange Hight Elfs!!! Lot of them have Robe (magic lore). Faction hit about Beffalen inhabitant,but as they died they say that they give there lives for the dark lady (neriak queen???). On the 3rd level there is an other new inky she is indifferent to me and answer to my Hail but not possible to go in any dialogue with her...<br>
By the same time a friend of my go to check in Black Burrows if something happen there, but no new troubles there.<br>
<br>
